{"type":"message","id":"a9b5fd84","parentId":"a301b3ec","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:38:53.439Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想看他的自选股，我现在已经有更新后的列表（包括新增的 BK1629 AI 应用板块），让我用 Tushare API 获取最新的实时数据。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，老板！您的自选股已经更新为 **15 只股票 +1 个概念板块** 了。让我帮您查询最新的实时行情:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6fcdbd9129264ffbb575688c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\n\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 从文件读取最新的自选股列表\nwith open('stock/watchlist.txt', 'r') as f:\n    stocks = [line.strip() for line in f if line.strip()]\n\nprint(\"=\"*120)\nprint(\"📊 您的自选股实时行情 (2026-03-09)\")\nprint(f\"持仓数量：{len(stocks)} 只\")\nprint(\"=\"*120)\n\ndata = []\nfor item in stocks:\n    parts = item.split('|')\n    code = parts[0]\n    name = parts[1] if len(parts) > 1 else \"\"\n    \n    try:\n        # 判断是否是概念板块 (BK 开头)\n        if code.startswith('BK'):\n            # 概念板块指数\n            df = pro.index_daily(ts_code=code, trade_date='20260309')\n            if not df.empty:\n                row = df.iloc[0]\n                data.append({\n                    '股票': f\"{code} | {name}\",\n                    '类型': '概念',\n                    '现价': row['close'],\n                    '涨跌幅': row['pct_chg'],\n                    '成交量': '-',\n                    '成交额': '-'\n                })\n        else:\n            # 个股\n            daily_df = pro.daily(trade_date='20260309', ts_code=code)\n            rt_df = pro.rt_min(ts_code=code, freq='5MIN')\n            \n            if not daily_df.empty and not rt_df.empty:\n                daily = daily_df.iloc[0]\n                data.append({\n                    '股票': f\"{code} | {name}\",\n                    '类型': '个股',\n                    '现价': daily['close'],\n                    '涨跌幅': daily['pct_chg'],\n                    '成交量': f\"{daily['vol']/10000:.2f}万手\",\n                    '成交额': f\"{daily['amount']/10000000:.2f}亿\"\n                })\n    except Exception as e:\n        pass\n\ndf_result = pd.DataFrame(data)\nif not df_result.empty:\n    print(df_result.to_string(index=False))\n\nprint(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*120)\nprint(f\"✅ 成功获取 {len(df_result)} 只股票的行情数据\")\nprint(f\"📈 数据来源：Tushare API\")\nprint(\"=\"*120)\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773049126133}}
